  <brief_title>EC95 of Remifentanil for Preventing Cough</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predicted EC95 of Effect-site Concentration of Remifentanil for Preventing Cough After Laryngomicrosurgery From Propofol Anesthesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
